en_250186_0	The group of Senior Non-Commissioned Officers (SNCOs) of Bangladesh Army who are in Sri Lanka on a familiarization tour under the Army Commander-initiated Army to Army cooperation for SNCOs went to Minneriya Infantry Training Centre (ITC) on Wednesday (14).
en_250186_1	Nine SNCOs, led by two Officers of the Bangladesh Army were welcomed and shown around the premises where All Ranks are trained for infantry roles.
en_250186_2	Major General Suraj Bansajaya, Commandant ITC before they were taken round the premises presented them with a comprehensive briefing on roles and tasks of the ITC.
